# Analisis Bug Loan Prospect: GetX (1235) vs Riverpod (1234)

Laporan mendalam perbandingan kode antara versi GetX (`feature/TASK-1235-Getx-upgrade`) dan versi Riverpod (`feature/TASK-1234-migrations-state-refactor`) terkait 8 bug yang dilaporkan pada fitur **Loan Prospect**.

---

## Ringkasan Temuan

| Bug ID | Judul | Root Cause | Severity |
|--------|-------|------------|----------|
| M01.F01.12 | Birthdate tidak ada action | [CustomDateTimePicker](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/components/custom/custom_date_time_picker.dart#12-75) — kemungkinan issue di widget level atau state tidak ter-rebuild | 🟡 Medium |
| M01.F01.13 | Industry Sub Sector tidak muncul | [CustomIndustry](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/components/custom/custom_industry.dart#11-33) menggunakan **global** LOV provider tanpa tag scoping | 🔴 High |
| M01.F01.14 | Tidak bisa pindah form setelah Capacity | [onTabTapped](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/loanprospect/page/loanprospect_new_detail_entity_page.dart#127-145) validasi form blocking — `monthlyIncome` validator trigger | 🔴 High |
| M01.F01.15 | Tidak bisa save — "Monthly Income cannot empty" | Validator `formUtil.veriftextFieldIsNotNull` pada Monthly Income form Capacity | 🔴 High |
| M01.F01.16 | Pick point domisili entity tidak muncul | `pickLocation: false` pada `showMap()` entity — bukan pick, hanya view | 🟡 Medium |
| M01.F01.17 | List kab/kota entity tidak muncul | LOV address detail dependency chain — provider scope entity | 🟡 Medium |
| M01.F01.18 | Document form entity force closed | [doAdd()](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/common/widget/list_document.dart#97-119) di [ListDocument](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/common/widget/list_document.dart#30-36) — race condition provider initialization | 🔴 High |
| M01.F01.19 | Document form tidak terbuka | [doRefresh()](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/common/widget/list_document.dart#53-92) fallback logic — provider try-catch silently fails | 🔴 High |

