## M01.F01.12 — Birthdate Tidak Ada Action

### Lokasi Kode
- [individual_dtl.dart:437-465](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/bizpartner/widget/individual_dtl.dart#L437-L465)
- [custom_date_time_picker.dart](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/components/custom/custom_date_time_picker.dart)

### Analisis
Di versi Riverpod, [CustomDateTimePicker](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/components/custom/custom_date_time_picker.dart#12-75) dipanggil dengan parameter:
```dart
CustomDateTimePicker(
  fieldName: 'birthDate',
  newDate: birthDate,           // local DateTime? variable
  onDateChanged: (newDate) {
    birthDate = newDate;
    setState(() {});            // rebuild UI
  },
  firstState: birthDate == null,
  onValidator: formUtil.verifDateNotNull,
  onClear: () {
    birthDate = null;
    setState(() {});
  },
  enableClear: true,
)
```

### Kemungkinan Root Cause
1. **`setState` tanpa Riverpod rebuild**: `birthDate` adalah variabel lokal (`DateTime? birthDate` line 49), bukan bagian dari provider state. `setState` seharusnya cukup, tetapi jika widget tree di-rebuild dari parent via provider, local state bisa hilang.
2. **[_syncRxFromProvider](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/bizpartner/widget/entity_dtl.dart#87-110) hanya satu arah**: Data dari provider state disinkronkan ke local field saat [initState](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/components/custom/custom_industry.dart#36-68), tapi perubahan local `birthDate` tidak di-push kembali ke provider state sampai [updateValue()](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/common/widget/list_document.dart#93-96) dipanggil.
3. **Widget [CustomDateTimePicker](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/components/custom/custom_date_time_picker.dart#12-75) sendiri** — perlu cek apakah [_selectDate(context)](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/components/custom/custom_date_time_picker.dart#164-328) method berjalan dengan benar pasca migrasi.

### Perbandingan GetX
Di GetX, `birthDate` adalah **`Rx<DateTime?>`** — setiap perubahan otomatis merebuild widget melalui `Obx`. Di Riverpod, perubahan bergantung pada `setState` local yang lebih rapuh.

