## M01.F01.13 — Industry Sub Sector Tidak Menampilkan Data

### Lokasi Kode
- [custom_industry.dart](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/components/custom/custom_industry.dart)
- [individual_dtl_capacity.dart:543-549](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/bizpartner/widget/individual_dtl_capacity.dart#L543-L549)

### Analisis
```dart
// individual_dtl_capacity.dart:543
CustomIndustry(
  tag: tagIndustry,
  industrySectorVal: state.selectedIndustriSectore,
  industrySubSectorVal: state.selectedIndustriSubSector,
)
```

[CustomIndustry](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/components/custom/custom_industry.dart#11-33) internally menggunakan **global providers**:
```dart
// custom_industry.dart:initState
ref.read(lovIndustrySectoreNotifierProvider.notifier)
    .selectIndustrySectore(widget.industrySectorVal!);
ref.read(lovIndustrySubSectoreNotifierProvider.notifier)
    .setParentAndFetch(
      parentIdParam: int.parse(widget.industrySectorVal!.id!),
      ...
    );
```

### Root Cause
> **`lovIndustrySubSectoreNotifierProvider` adalah provider global tanpa tag/family parameter**. Jika widget lain (seperti entity capacity, employment, atau self-employee) juga menggunakan LOV Industry, state akan **saling menimpa**.

Di GetX, setiap widget memiliki controller instance terpisah karena binding system. Di Riverpod, provider global yang sama di-share oleh semua consumer.

Selain itu, `setParentAndFetch` dipanggil di [initState](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/components/custom/custom_industry.dart#36-68) via `Future.microtask`. Jika `selectedIndustriSectore` belum ter-populate karena provider belum siap, `parentIdParam` bisa null/invalid → sub sector list kosong.

> [!CAUTION]
> Tag `tagIndustry` pada `CustomIndustry.tag` diterima tapi **TIDAK DIGUNAKAN** di widget internal. LOV provider tetap global.

