## M01.F01.15 — Monthly Income Cannot Empty Saat Save

### Lokasi Kode
- [individual_dtl_capacity.dart:326-361](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/bizpartner/widget/individual_dtl_capacity.dart#L326-L361)

### Analisis
```dart
CustomTextField(
  fieldName: 'monthly-income',
  ...
  controller: monthlyIncomeController,
  onValidator: formUtil.veriftextFieldIsNotNull,  // ← WAJIB!
)
```

### Root Cause
`Monthly Income` di tab Capacity memiliki validator `veriftextFieldIsNotNull` yang artinya **mandatory**. Masalah:

1. User mengisi form di tab lain (Detail, dll.)
2. User pindah ke Capacity tab (atau navigasi trigger [_updateAllForm](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/loanprospect/page/loanprospect_new_detail_entity_page.dart#227-250))
3. [_updateAllForm()](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/loanprospect/page/loanprospect_new_detail_entity_page.dart#227-250) memanggil `entityDtlCapacityKey.currentState!.updateValue()`
4. [updateValue()](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/common/widget/list_document.dart#93-96) menjalankan `formKey.currentState?.validate()` → validator `monthlyIncome` fire → fail karena kosong
5. Return false → block save

**Tapi ada inkonsistensi**: di [_updateAllForm](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/loanprospect/page/loanprospect_new_detail_entity_page.dart#227-250) entity page, hanya [EntityDtl](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/bizpartner/widget/entity_dtl.dart#27-33) yang return value-nya digunakan:
```dart
isValid = await entityDtlKey.currentState!.updateValue();
// Capacity updateValue() dipanggil tapi return value-nya DIABAIKAN:
await entityDtlCapacityKey.currentState!.updateValue();
```

Jadi **save seharusnya tetap bisa** karena Capacity validation result tidak mempengaruhi `isValid`. Bug mungkin terjadi karena:
- Form validator menampilkan error visual "Monthly Income cannot empty" yang membingungkan user
- Atau ada flow di **individual detail** (bukan entity) yang memiliki logic berbeda

> [!WARNING]
> Ini bug **UX** — validator visual muncul meskipun save tetap proceed. Atau ada code path lain yang memblock.

