## M01.F01.18 & M01.F01.19 — Document Form Tidak Terbuka / Force Close

### Lokasi Kode
- [list_document.dart:37-91](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/common/widget/list_document.dart#L37-L91) — [doRefresh()](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/common/widget/list_document.dart#53-92)
- [list_document.dart:97-118](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/common/widget/list_document.dart#L97-L118) — [doAdd()](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/common/widget/list_document.dart#97-119)
- [loanprospect_new_detail_entity_page.dart:165](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/loanprospect/page/loanprospect_new_detail_entity_page.dart#L165)

### Analisis
[ListDocument](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/common/widget/list_document.dart#30-36) di [initState](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/components/custom/custom_industry.dart#36-68) langsung memanggil [doRefresh()](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/common/widget/list_document.dart#53-92):
```dart
@override
void initState() {
  super.initState();
  _documentService = ref.read(documentServiceProvider);
  doRefresh();
}
```

[doRefresh()](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/common/widget/list_document.dart#53-92) menggunakan **triple try-catch fallback**:
```dart
Future<void> doRefresh() async {
  try {
    // 1. Coba baca dari BizPartnerDetailNotifier
    final bizPartnerState = ref.read(bizPartnerDetailNotifierProvider);
    // ...
  } catch (e) {}  // ← SILENTLY IGNORED
  
  try {
    // 2. Coba baca dari LoanprospectEntityPage
    final entityState = ref.read(loanprospectEntityPageNotifierProvider);
    // ...
  } catch (e) {}  // ← SILENTLY IGNORED
  
  try {
    // 3. Coba baca dari ApplicationPageNotifier
    final appState = ref.read(applicationPageNotifierProvider);
    // ...
  } catch (e) {}  // SILENTLY IGNORED
}
```

### Root Cause
> **Race Condition**: `loanprospectEntityPageNotifierProvider` di-init di `Future.microtask()` pada parent page (line 66 entity detail page), tetapi [ListDocument](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/common/widget/list_document.dart#30-36) (tab 6) juga menjalankan [initState](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/components/custom/custom_industry.dart#36-68) sebelum microtask selesai. Akibatnya, `entityState.entityModel` masih null → `reffNo` null.

Ketika user menekan tombol add document:
```dart
void doAdd() async {
  var reslt = await context.push(RouteName.documentDetail, extra: {
    'doc-from': docFrom,  // null jika doRefresh gagal
    'list-docs': models,  // kosong
  });
  if (reslt is DocsModel) {
    docModel.docAttahReffno = reffNo;  // null → crash di service call!
    lstDocResult = await _documentService.putAttachDoc(docModel); // BOOM!
  }
}
```

Flow crash:
1. `reffNo = null` karena provider belum ready
2. `putAttachDoc` API call dengan `reffNo = null` → error/crash
3. **Force close** (unhandled exception)

### Perbandingan GetX
Di GetX, `ListDocumentController` membaca data dari `Get.find<>()` yang dijamin exist karena binding hierarchy. Di Riverpod, provider global autoDispose bisa belum ter-init saat child widget dibuat.

> [!CAUTION]
> Bug kritis — menyebabkan force close. [doAdd()](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/common/widget/list_document.dart#97-119) tidak memiliki null-check pada `reffNo` sebelum memanggil API.

---

## Rekomendasi Perbaikan

| Priority | Bug | Fix |
|----------|-----|-----|
| 🔴 P0 | M01.F01.18/19 | Tambah null-check `reffNo` di [doAdd()](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/common/widget/list_document.dart#97-119), perbaiki timing init provider |
| 🔴 P0 | M01.F01.14/15 | Ubah [onTabTapped](file:///Users/asix/Documents/proyek_flutter/mobile-los-new/lib/app/loanprospect/page/loanprospect_new_detail_entity_page.dart#127-145) agar tidak block navigasi, atau pisahkan validate vs save |
| 🔴 P1 | M01.F01.13 | Implementasi `family` provider untuk `lovIndustrySubSectoreNotifierProvider` agar scoped per widget |
| 🟡 P1 | M01.F01.12 | Investigasi `CustomDateTimePicker._selectDate` — cek apakah dialog builder bekerja |
| 🟡 P2 | M01.F01.16 | Ubah `pickLocation: false` → `true` jika memang perlu pick, atau cek requirement |
| 🟡 P2 | M01.F01.17 | Pastikan cascade LOV dependency (province→kab/kota) ter-init sebelum render |
